data.description: Welcome to 3297 Greystone Road. Located on a corner lot, this home has a bigger lot than the standard home. Walking into the home, you will notice new flooring throughout the home, tall ceilings and plenty of room for entertaining. The kitchen has been fully remodeled, plenty of cabinet space and counter space that is a luxury to have. Entering the backyard, you will notice the pool and spa located perfectly where you can relax and enjoy the views of this backyard overlooking trees and mountains. This home has a formal dining room, family room with a gas fireplace, first floor bedroom and bathroom. Upstairs you'll find 4 bedrooms and a grand Primary Bedroom and Bathroom. Located next to award winning schools, this is a perfect property.
